headline: Dow Jones Futures Rise; Dow Above 50K With Apple, Boeing, These AI Stocks New Buys. But Market Is Still Divided.
summary: The Dow has topped 50,000 for the first time, with JPMorgan, Apple and Boeing in buy areas. The Nasdaq is still below key support, but these AI stocks are reviving.

headline: Scott Strazik on How GE Vernova Is Riding the AI Power Surge
summary: When Scott Strazik became head of General Electric’s energy business, GE Vernova, in 2021, the electricity business felt very different than it does today.
